snippet.title: Evercade - Delphine Software Collection 1 - Trailer
snippet.description:
Delphine Software Collection 1 brings four stunning games to Evercade with Amiga and console classics on one physical collection!

Available September 2023
Pre-order from July 2023

Find out more:  https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/delphine-software-collection-1/

Full Games List:
Another World (Amiga)
Flashback (Console)
Future Wars (Amiga)
Operation Stealth (Amiga)
